text: ♪The wheels on the bus go               round and round♪
♪round and round♪
♪round and round♪
♪The wheels on the bus go        round and round♪
♪All day long♪
♪The wipers on the bus go        swish, swish, swish♪
♪swish swish swish♪
♪swish swish swish♪
♪The wipers on the bus go        swish, swish, swish♪
♪All Day Long♪
♪The horn on the bus goes       beep beep beep♪
♪beep beep beep♪
♪The horn on the bus goes       beep beep beep♪
♪All day long♪
♪The mummies on the bus go        natter natter natter,        natter natter natter,        natter natter natter.       The mummies on the bus go         natter natter natter,       all day long.♪
♪The froggies on the bus        jump up and down,        up and down,        up and down,       The froggies on the bus         jump up and down,       all day long.♪
♪The birdies on the bus go        tweet, tweet tweet,        tweet tweet tweet,        tweet tweet tweet.       The birdies on the bus go         tweet, tweet, tweet       all day long.♪
Oh Dear!
♪The man in the van goes       fix fix fix,        fix fix fix,        fix fix fix,       The man in the van goes         fix fix fix,       all day long.♪
♪The wheels on the bus go round and round,        round and round,       round and round,        The wheels on the bus go round and round,       all day long.♪
